title: Video Release: Coast Guard monitors rescue of mariner 400 miles south of Cold Bay, Alaska ...
text: ( Source : USCG - United States Coast Guard ) Motor vessel Tor Viking crew rescues a distressed mariner from his disabled 30-foot sailboat approximately 400 miles south of Cold Bay, Alaska , Oct. 20, 2015 . The mariner alerted the U.S. Coast
